            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:14855058-fb34-4309-8240-9e4c00986701</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/talent_management/~3/WY8QL5s3fGA/Psychological-effects-job-loss</link>
